    {
      "id": "552b3fbe-7b82-49f1-91cf-d027821b1e63",
      "title": "Can't Marry Mary",
      "url": "http://www.worldanvil.com/world/secret/552b3fbe-7b82-49f1-91cf-d027821b1e63/edit",
      "content": "“@[[b]Lord Collin Davenport[/b]](person:9c8d167e-e8b4-42a4-9c23-3b2af707de87) has quite forbidden anyone from courting @[[b]Lady Mary Davenport[/b]](person:4b285322-9a2b-4ada-97b8-f0ea5f6e75a9), even though it’s been a few years since her debut. Rumor has it he dueled the last man that tried. If he weren’t from such a respectable family, one might worry there were inappropriate affections afoot.”"
    },
