    {
      "id": "451d3b3c-5047-468b-838e-7dfeb5183fb3",
      "title": "Knightley Sighs for Love",
      "url": "http://www.worldanvil.com/world/secret/451d3b3c-5047-468b-838e-7dfeb5183fb3/edit",
      "content": "“@[[b]Knightley[/b]](person:032dc6b7-44ea-49dc-a76b-a2e0b59de07a) is in love. Just look at the way they sigh, the idle looks they give. I wonder what young woman has caught their attentions. And what they intend to do to win her...”"
    },
    {
      "id": "fbb24a56-9423-4834-9dda-3314a49662a7",
      "title": "Lady Priestly's Marriage",
      "url": "http://www.worldanvil.com/world/secret/fbb24a56-9423-4834-9dda-3314a49662a7/edit",
      "content": "“@[[b]Lady Francesca Priestly[/b]](person:17492303-aecb-4f1b-a6a6-19a31b5d50e9) and her husband, @[Lord Frederick Priestly](person:c5d30415-be40-4b06-9f94-05c9a0644e7c), have been estranged these last twenty years. He’s a philanderer, committed adultery with half the Ton. He left for the country house and hasn’t been seen in London since. Well, I certainly wouldn’t be anywhere Lady Priestly didn’t want me, that’s for certain. That woman is a force.”"
    },
    {
      "id": "9110f4fc-1ff2-48d8-8bd1-ee968a5b6897",
      "title": "Mr. Murray's Sharpe Disappearance",
      "url": "http://www.worldanvil.com/world/secret/9110f4fc-1ff2-48d8-8bd1-ee968a5b6897/edit",
      "content": "“Long ago, @[[b]Mr. Edwin Murray[/b]](person:e401c266-3f1a-43e2-874d-f5f2e026e04d) disappeared into the country for several months. It would have predated @[[b]Miss Amelia Murray[/b]](person:81818c4e-8ba3-4316-aa44-a49a65d8df06)’s birth considerably, but I always wonder... @[Miss Mildred Sharpe](person:abfead6a-b240-4f08-aeec-ececcc46a217) went missing around that time as well, didn’t she? Those two were always bosom companions.”"
    },
    {
      "id": "7ed556b2-c45b-49be-a987-0838ef1fe834",
      "title": "Laurie Fiddled and Prewitt House Burned",
      "url": "http://www.worldanvil.com/world/secret/7ed556b2-c45b-49be-a987-0838ef1fe834/edit",
      "content": "“@[[b]Major Radcliffe[/b]](person:adaab4af-763b-4b42-8c38-2d98f70245ad), @[[b]Lt. Foxsmith[/b]](person:71777950-6f6e-41ce-896c-ce17f10a5752), @[[b]Lt. Spencer[/b]](person:122186c2-774a-43a4-9c26-ba067474ca78), and @[[b]Major Osbourne[/b]](person:8fe90b6d-2b6d-4c71-bbc5-a616ebe5fbea) are inseparable.  I heard they were all drunk out of their heads the night that Prewitt House, where the Spencer family lives, burned, and that Lt. Foxsmith saved their lives... and @[[b]Miss Spencer[/b]](person:0fb14ae9-02eb-41ff-bd68-02036ee7b950)’s, too!”"
    },
    {
      "id": "f5a9f1de-50ae-49e8-959c-b87aa3b00bea",
      "title": "Murray's Mentees",
      "url": "http://www.worldanvil.com/world/secret/f5a9f1de-50ae-49e8-959c-b87aa3b00bea/edit",
      "content": "[b]@[Miss Amelia Murray](person:81818c4e-8ba3-4316-aa44-a49a65d8df06)[/b] has two young proteges, [b]@[Miss Bridget Cross](person:0ff4f577-7cc0-45f2-97b0-f0311b8a3ab1)[/b] and [b]@[Miss Fanny Clark](person:6021bf56-fa01-4b78-acc3-faca295882fb)[/b] that she is trying to get married off. Difficult matches - Miss Cross is so plain and uncomfortable, even with her fortune. And Miss Clark is poor, so even her notable good looks might not win her a husband worth having..."
    },
