    },
    {
      "id": "f7181276-cbe4-4d65-8eee-aca4cc5234b7",
      "url": "https://www.worldanvil.com/world/secret/f7181276-cbe4-4d65-8eee-aca4cc5234b7/edit",
      "content": "“@[[b]Miss Harrington[/b]](person:0b7871c8-470e-44a2-adfd-df2563988cd9) is quite compromised by @[[b]Miss Wickham[/b]](person:6741985b-16a9-4206-bc70-7218ff09b56d). Miss Wickham much overshadows her in beauty, wit, and grace. I doubt Miss Harrington will ever escape from her shadow.”",
      "title": "Wickham Overshadowing Harrington"
    },
    {
      "id": "7d3f0d77-afc7-4aef-a806-b2166dbc5181",
      "url": "https://www.worldanvil.com/world/secret/7d3f0d77-afc7-4aef-a806-b2166dbc5181/edit",
      "content": "“@[[b]Mr. Willoughby[/b]](person:90d47ebf-ef1f-4a8a-b2e5-b205034a6e53) has been cursing @[[b]Captain Thompson[/b]](person:1b5f78ae-c59b-4fa6-8cee-b69606c9f3dd)’s name the last few weeks, and I’ve heard might challenge him to a duel – Mr. Willoughby is so gentle, I wonder what on earth he’s done.”",
      "title": "Willoughby and the Cad Captain"
    },
    {
      "id": "58a1785f-7673-4468-bba6-f4057b859bf3",
      "url": "https://www.worldanvil.com/world/secret/58a1785f-7673-4468-bba6-f4057b859bf3/edit",
      "content": "“@[[b]Miss Willoughby[/b]](person:df302dbc-d965-4444-876d-a88248a7063e) wore a matching gown to @[[b]Miss Thompson[/b]](person:f1d29e0d-c70b-4c29-8338-d70578f5bea9) at the premiere ball of the season- how embarrassing! She must be particularly cross about it, as Miss Willoughby considers herself something of a woman of fashion.”",
      "title": "Willoughby and Thompson Match Gowns"
    },
    {
      "id": "027bef3a-4c3a-464f-94ac-7711b841260d",
      "url": "https://www.worldanvil.com/world/secret/027bef3a-4c3a-464f-94ac-7711b841260d/edit",
      "content": "“I’ve heard that @[[b]Miss Willoughby[/b]](person:df302dbc-d965-4444-876d-a88248a7063e) and @[[b]Lt. Foxsmith[/b]](person:71777950-6f6e-41ce-896c-ce17f10a5752) became engaged this month past. He’s far below her in wealth and status, but stranger things have happened I suppose. @[[b]Lord Collin Davenport[/b]](person:9c8d167e-e8b4-42a4-9c23-3b2af707de87) is positively stewing about it, as it has long been assumed he and Miss Willoughby would wed someday.”",
      "title": "Willoughby Snares a Foxsmith"
    },
    {
      "id": "95ab4350-3842-4880-96e7-9feda4750092",
      "url": "https://www.worldanvil.com/world/secret/95ab4350-3842-4880-96e7-9feda4750092/edit",
      "content": "“Quite the catch, @[[b]Miss Adrianne Sharpe[/b]](person:cec0b747-8c34-42a7-ad3e-9f87f4826597). I heard from @[[b]Mr. Harrington[/b]](person:4d6031ee-b918-44a8-b4fc-92222113a6d4) that her father was an incredibly wealthy man with the East India Company, and now that he’s dead she stands to inherit his whole fortune. She only inherits once she’s married, of course, due to some stipulation in the will- so she’s eager to do so, now that she’s in England. Born in Calcutta- her grandmother on her father’s side was Indian, so I’m told. This must all be incredibly new to her. And now to have to live with the dreadful spinster @[[b]Miss Hester Sharpe[/b]](person:da9cc467-54f1-4d2c-9371-e6790135beb2)!”",
      "title": "Young Miss Sharpe's Company"
    }
    ]
  }